      <title>交易员认为美联储降息半个百分点的可能性大于降息四分之一个百分点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/dollar-slides-near-lowest-since-january-on-large-fed-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员再次认为，美联储决策者在本周会议上将利率下调半个百分点而非四分之一个百分点的可能性更大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/dollar-slides-near-lowest-since-january-on-large-fed-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 04:26:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
